  "response_text": "# Weekly Meal & Fitness Plan\n\n## 🏋️ FITNESS SCHEDULE\n\n| Day | Workout | Duration | Intensity |\n|-----|---------|----------|-----------|\n| **Monday** | Upper Body Strength | 45 min | High |\n| **Tuesday** | Cardio (Running/Cycling) | 30 min | Moderate |\n| **Wednesday** | Rest or Yoga | 20-30 min | Low |\n| **Thursday** | Lower Body Strength | 45 min | High |\n| **Friday** | HIIT Training | 30 min | High |\n| **Saturday** | Active Recovery (Walk/Swim) | 30-45 min | Low |\n| **Sunday** | Rest Day | — | — |\n\n---\n\n## 🍽️ MEAL PLAN\n\n### **MONDAY**\n- **Breakfast:** Oatmeal with berries & almonds\n- **Lunch:** Grilled chicken, brown rice, broccoli\n- **Dinner:** Baked salmon, sweet potato, asparagus\n- **Snack:** Greek yogurt with honey\n\n### **TUESDAY**\n- **Breakfast:** Scrambled eggs, whole wheat toast, avocado\n- **Lunch:** Turkey sandwich, mixed greens, apple\n- **Dinner:** Lean ground beef tacos, beans, salsa\n- **Snack:** Protein shake, banana\n\n### **WEDNESDAY**\n- **Breakfast:** Greek yogurt parfait with granola\n- **Lunch:** Quinoa bowl with chickpeas & vegetables\n- **Dinner:** Grilled chicken breast, pasta, marinara\n- **Snack:** Almonds, orange\n\n### **THURSDAY**\n- **Breakfast:** Smoothie (spinach, protein, berries, almond milk)\n- **Lunch:** Tuna salad with olive oil dressing\n- **Dinner:** Baked cod, roasted vegetables, rice\n- **Snack:** Cottage cheese with pineapple\n\n### **FRIDAY**\n- **Breakfast:** Whole grain pancakes with berries\n- **Lunch:** Grilled chicken wrap, hummus, vegetables\n- **Dinner:** Lean steak, sweet potato, green beans\n- **Snack:** Protein bar, almonds\n\n### **SATURDAY**\n- **Breakfast:** Veggie omelet with whole wheat toast\n- **Lunch:** Lentil soup, side salad\n- **Dinner:** Grilled chicken, quinoa, roasted Brussels sprouts\n- **Snack:** Greek yogurt, berries\n\n### **SUNDAY**\n- **Breakfast:** Avocado toast on whole grain bread\n- **Lunch:** Vegetable stir-fry with tofu/chicken\n- **Dinner:** Turkey meatballs, whole wheat pasta\n- **Snack:** Mixed nuts, fruit\n\n---\n\n## 💡 TIPS FOR SUCCESS\n\n✅ **Hydration:** Drink 8-10 glasses of water daily\n✅ **Meal Prep:** Prepare meals on Sunday for the week\n✅ **Sleep:** Aim for 7-9 hours nightly\n✅ **Flexibility:** Adjust based on your preferences & goals\n✅ **Progress:** Track workouts and measurements weekly\n\n---\n\n*Customize this plan based on your dietary restrictions, fitness level, and goals!*",
